Travel junkie with a penchant for spontaneous road trips. Last minute plans? Count me in! By day, I’m a software engineer, but by night, I’m exploring new cuisines and adding to my plant collection. Recently got into pottery—let's swap DIY project ideas!

Caffeine addict and aspiring novelist. I thrive in chaotic environments and love a good debate. Yoga keeps me grounded, and live music keeps me energized. Ever wonder why people say 'cheese' when taking pictures? Let's ponder over a cup of coffee!

Museum curator with a love for ancient history and modern art. Weekend plans often involve gallery hopping or discovering new hiking spots. Quirky habit: I always carry a sketchbook. If you could live in any historical period, which one would you choose?

Fitness enthusiast and professional dancer. My world revolves around music and movement. Sushi and sunsets make me happy. Dreaming of visiting every continent—Antarctica, you’re next! What’s the most spontaneous thing you’ve ever done?
